":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T18:36:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>堅持左咁耐終於識得放棄<br />\n放棄左雖然好唔開心好唔捨得<br />\n但成身鬆晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個人都覺得輕左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者係我以前睇野太窄<br />\n都係放左手先有機會見到更好既可能性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加油，巴打，我都係比人反左面先識得放低，根本一開始唔應該做朋友，因為我係人地心目中只不過係過客</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁 一定有d導火線先會醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60115a0f596605b5b928bc7c542b3bacfed7b293","tid":88681,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T18:55:32.000Z","msg":"我仲未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a03bf27c54f3711d5ec007f434cb7e3fa2a51082","tid":88681,"uid":24589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T18:57:56.000Z","msg":"放手了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9219fddcca70ac54c54d614e07a1ab8bc64d03d","tid":88681,"uid":68981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T19:17:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36bd0368419b669d323ab3f36eab426e5ab96567","tid":88681,"uid":41859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T19:50:21.000Z","msg":"捉自己捉得太緊"},{"pid":"5ef4c5b6627e013cce85c63cce1a822559f0ee88","tid":88681,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T19:55:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就算隻手火燒咁 我都唔會放架喇</blockquote><br />\n點算呀 我又有返呢種感覺<br />\n又想繼續玩火<br />\n放手咁難既點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f939afc7885be833ae244bd63995ba240c8eb0c7","tid":88681,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl